{
  "stem": "24268.4",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, going back to when I quit, I still got the letter from Mr.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Paul Shore.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I never forget.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was the vice president of the associate from South-- South Bend.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I received a letter, if anyone said anything to me, and if I'd like to change to another department, they would be glad to do.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So they come.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I was a good worker, obviously, because all the auditors when they came, they said since we have Rose, everything is perfect, and all the things.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I could sense there was a lot in our surrounding, there were a few one that were lovely people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Matter of fact, I still receive-- but she was working in the legal department, not where I was-- I still get Christmas and Hanukkah card.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I still receive now-- Ethel Krinberg, such a wonderful lady.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That's, you know, makes you feel that the world is not lost.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There are still good people in it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I wish there would be more of them like her, because wonderful people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we still correspond with each other.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My grandchildren-- I think my have the greatest grandchildren.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody love my daughter, naturally, but I'm going now to the second generation, which I think I'm proud of them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I'm grateful to God that he blessed us at least with some comfort to have those two boys.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Which they're very devoted, very good, not only for us, but I think they are so sincere.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There are not too many young people you find them today, they respect their pay for grandparents, for parents, for anyone.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they are very intelligent.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Matter of fact--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Name is Zaron-- the oldest is Zaron.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He just graduate from Michigan with seven honors.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
